CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, January 26, 1946, pg. 13, reads: "Gunning for 'Y' - The classy Young Men's A. C. basketball team of Beaver Falls will be the 'Y' Big Five's opponents here Friday night. The 'Y' team has been hitting a fast stride, and hopes to add this crack team to their list of victims."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of Beaver Falls A. C. men's basketball team, including numbers 6, 8, 14, 3, 4, 11, and 10, posed in Centre Avenue YMCA
